msgctxt "56_Zhao"
msgid "So what kept you today? I thought you'd be here earlier."
msgstr "So what kept you today? I thought you'd be here earlier."

msgctxt "68_Tanimura"
msgid "This detective, Sugiuchi-san, was grilling me back at the station. Ever since that shooting, Homicide's been all up in my ass."
msgstr "This detective, Sugiuchi-san, was grilling me back at the station. Ever since that shooting, Homicide's been all up in my ass."

msgctxt "80_Zhao"
msgid "Hah, police questioning police? That's ridiculous."
msgstr "¿Ah, la policía cuestiona a la policía? Es ridículo."

msgctxt "92_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, normally I wouldn't give a damn... But apparently, this wasn't just one random punk killing another."
msgstr "Yeah, normally I wouldn't give a damn... But apparently, this wasn't just one random punk killing another."

msgctxt "104_Tanimura"
msgid "It was significant enough to set the Tojo Clan against itself."
msgstr "It was significant enough to set the Tojo Clan against itself."

msgctxt "116_Tanimura"
msgid "...Although why Homicide cares so much about mob activity is beyond me. That's what Organized Crime's for."
msgstr "...Although why Homicide cares so much about mob activity is beyond me. That's what Organized Crime's for."

msgctxt "128_Zhao"
msgid "Either way, we don't need another gang war in this city..."
msgstr "De cualquier manera, no necesitamos otra guerra entre bandas en esta ciudad..."

msgctxt "140_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh, and it's not just the Tojo Clan. I hear the Ueno Seiwa's involved."
msgstr "Oh, y no es solo el Clan Tojo. He oído que el Clan Ueno Seiwa también está involucrado."

msgctxt "152_Zhao"
msgid "Ueno Seiwa? Wait, isn't that...?"
msgstr "Ueno Seiwa? Wait, isn't that...?"

msgctxt "164_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah. The same clan my dad was investigating after the Yoshiharu Ueno hit... Right around when he was murdered."
msgstr "Yeah. The same clan my dad was investigating after the Yoshiharu Ueno hit... Right around when he was murdered."

msgctxt "176_Zhao"
msgid "...You think this is connected somehow?"
msgstr "...You think this is connected somehow?"

msgctxt "188_Tanimura"
msgid "Can't say. All I know is the Ueno Seiwa Clan's been quiet for 25 years..."
msgstr "Can't say. All I know is the Ueno Seiwa Clan's been quiet for 25 years..."

msgctxt "200_Tanimura"
msgid "But now there's this shooting a week ago, and suddenly they've gone into overdrive? Something's definitely up."
msgstr "But now there's this shooting a week ago, and suddenly they've gone into overdrive? Something's definitely up."

msgctxt "212_Tanimura"
msgid "Following this case could lead me to someone who knows the truth... about who killed my dad."
msgstr "Following this case could lead me to someone who knows the truth... about who killed my dad."

msgctxt "224_Zhao"
msgid "You still looking for that woman?"
msgstr "You still looking for that woman?"

msgctxt "236_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, Yasuko Saejima. Her brother Taiga's the one who carried out the hit on Ueno."
msgstr "Yeah, Yasuko Saejima. Her brother Taiga's the one who carried out the hit on Ueno."

msgctxt "248_Tanimura"
msgid "She's been missing ever since that went down."
msgstr "She's been missing ever since that went down."

msgctxt "260_Zhao"
msgid "And you really think this Yasuko Saejima knows why your father was killed?"
msgstr "And you really think this Yasuko Saejima knows why your father was killed?"

msgctxt "272_Tanimura"
msgid "Maybe, maybe not. But the last thing written in his notebook was, \"Meet with Yasuko Saejima.\" That has to mean something."
msgstr "Maybe, maybe not. But the last thing written in his notebook was, \"Meet with Yasuko Saejima.\" That has to mean something."

msgctxt "284_Zhao"
msgid "So she might even be the last person who saw him alive..."
msgstr "So she might even be the last person who saw him alive..."

msgctxt "296_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "332_Manager of Midori"
msgid "Is this Tanimura?"
msgstr "Is this Tanimura?"

msgctxt "344_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, speaking."
msgstr "Yeah, speaking."

msgctxt "356_Manager of Midori"
msgid "This is Park, the manager at Midori."
msgstr "Este es Park, el manager de Midori."

msgctxt "368_Tanimura"
msgid "Midori? Oh, right, the Korean salon. What do you want?"
msgstr "Midori? Oh, right, the Korean salon. What do you want?"

msgctxt "380_Manager of Midori"
msgid "Can you come here as soon as possible?"
msgstr "Can you come here as soon as possible?"

msgctxt "392_Tanimura"
msgid "Why, the police raiding the place or something?"
msgstr "Why, the police raiding the place or something?"

msgctxt "404_Manager of Midori"
msgid "No, nothing like that. It's about that woman\\r\n"\n"you've been looking for."
msgstr "No, nothing like that. It's about that woman\\r\n"\n"you've been looking for."

msgctxt "416_Manager of Midori"
msgid "Someone who looks just like her is here right now."
msgstr "Someone who looks just like her is here right now."

msgctxt "428_Tanimura"
msgid "Are you serious!?"
msgstr "Are you serious!?"

msgctxt "440_Manager of Midori"
msgid "That's why I'm calling! Hurry up, before she leaves."
msgstr "That's why I'm calling! Hurry up, before she leaves."

msgctxt "452_Tanimura"
msgid "Okay, be right there."
msgstr "Okay, be right there."

msgctxt "500_Zhao"
msgid "Something wrong?"
msgstr "¿Todo bien?"

msgctxt "512_Tanimura"
msgid "I knew it. That killing set something in motion. Zhao-san, I think I found her."
msgstr "I knew it. That killing set something in motion. Zhao-san, I think I found her."

msgctxt "524_Zhao"
msgid "Wait, the woman we were just talking about!?"
msgstr "Wait, the woman we were just talking about!?"

msgctxt "536_Tanimura"
msgid "I don't know if it's really her, but I've got no reason to doubt it."
msgstr "I don't know if it's really her, but I've got no reason to doubt it."

msgctxt "548_Zhao"
msgid "I see. Then I suggest you be careful."
msgstr "I see. Then I suggest you be careful."

msgctxt "560_Tanimura"
msgid "You think?"
msgstr "You think?"

msgctxt "572_Zhao"
msgid "I'm serious. You're telling me this woman shows up out of nowhere, right as the Ueno Seiwa make their biggest ruckus in 25 years?"
msgstr "I'm serious. You're telling me this woman shows up out of nowhere, right as the Ueno Seiwa make their biggest ruckus in 25 years?"

msgctxt "584_Zhao"
msgid "The timing's too perfect."
msgstr "The timing's too perfect."

msgctxt "596_Tanimura"
msgid "So you're saying she's involved somehow."
msgstr "So you're saying she's involved somehow."

msgctxt "608_Zhao"
msgid "Well, you're about to find out, aren't you? Now go. Find her before she disappears again."
msgstr "Well, you're about to find out, aren't you? Now go. Find her before she disappears again."

msgctxt "620_Tanimura"
msgid "Right."
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "704_Mei Hua"
msgid "You off and running already, Ma-chan?"
msgstr "You off and running already, Ma-chan?"

msgctxt "716_Tanimura"
msgid "Yep, business as usual. You know how it is."
msgstr "Yep, business as usual. You know how it is."

msgctxt "728_Mei Hua"
msgid "Let us know if you need anything, okay? You know you're always welcome here."
msgstr "Let us know if you need anything, okay? You know you're always welcome here."

msgctxt "740_Mei Hua"
msgid "After all, we couldn't be called Homeland if we weren't your home away from home!"
msgstr "After all, we couldn't be called Homeland if we weren't your home away from home!"

msgctxt "752_Tanimura"
msgid "That's sweet, Mei Hua. Thank you."
msgstr "That's sweet, Mei Hua. Thank you."

